      <title>萨瓦德尔拒绝收购提议后 BBVA 股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bbva-shares-rise-after-sabadell-rejects-takeover-proposal-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二上午，在萨瓦德尔拒绝了 BBVA 主动提出的收购提议后，西班牙 BBVA 银行的股价上涨了 1.9%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bbva-shares-rise-after-sabadell-rejects-takeover-proposal-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 08:10:34 GMT</pubDate>
