      <title>裕信银行在利润超出预期后提高投资者奖励目标</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/unicredit-raises-investor-reward-goal-after-profit-tops-forecast-2024-05-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit) 周二公布的季度净收入远高于预期，并进一步提高了资本水平，随后该行上调了今年的投资者回报预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/unicredit-raises-investor-reward-goal-after-profit-tops-forecast-2024-05-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 07:18:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
